"bindurl ^https://duckduckgo.com f hint -bc [class="module__more-at-bottom"]
"bindurl ^https://duckduckgo.com f hint -bc "#duckbar_static > li a"
bindurl youtu((\.be)|(be\.com)) f hint -J

